task.summary: Creating a test code in MainClass to verify if webdriver is working with all the webbrowsers.
Creating Exercise1 Class with methods "browserStart": open the browser. And method "codePause": to pause code execution and pause it 2 seconds.
Implementing "verifyPageTitle": Compare the text "My Store" with the actual page title. And "refreshPage": Reloads the actual page
Implementing "returnHomePage": go back in browser history and navigate to home page. And "Navigate to": navigates to google.com.sv
Implementing "compareURL": compares the actual URL with some String value. And "closeBrowser": close the actual browser window
Implementing exercise1 test on chrome web browser
Implementing exercise 2 with methods "findelementUsingText", search an element using LinkText command. And implementing "findelementUsingXpath", seach an element using Xpath
Implementing exercise 2 with methods "findelementUsingCSS", search an element using CSS selector. And implementing "ClickUsingXpath", press left click on an element with xpath selector

Implementing exercise 2 with methods "firstUsingXpath", select the first element of multiple elements using Xpath selector. And implementing "lastUsingXpath", select the lastone element of multiple elements using Xpath selector
